{"tid":1610271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好去糾纏狗開槍合唔合理 因為舉槍已經唔合理","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T17:08:38.000Z","uid":235465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86d095858b030c7f53a300f681faea4f32b00c77","tid":1610271,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:53:39.000Z","msg":"見到有記者或者手足一直屌狗開槍<br />\n但事實上應該屌唔只係開槍 而係先屌舉槍 再屌舉槍+開槍<br />\n最簡單 因為警察支真槍唔可以隨便舉<br />\n有片好清晰影到 受到襲擊之前 班狗已經舉左槍 其實已經極端唔合理<br />\n一黎 單單舉槍 已經有可能構成走火<br />\n二黎 用TM遊行為例 當初有人想搶槍 但事實上失敗左 因為佢個槍袋本身有防盜功能<br />\n但隨便舉槍其實減低左搶槍個難度 因為唔需要經過個防盜袋 只要我人夠你子彈多打到你訓低 我就有槍用<br />\n三黎 一路講開 防暴警身上套gear其實好厚 <span style=\"color: red;\">任何情況假設狗身上full gear 而對方唔係用槍情況下 都唔應該舉槍</span><br />\n更唔好論當時情況前線幾乎1狗對1人<br />\nli樣叫所謂&quot;合適,相對應武力&quot;<br />\n再加上防暴本身配備非致命武器 更加唔應該使用有可能致命實彈<br />\n<br />\n簡單總結 開槍唔合理 但當時更加唔合理 其實係以當時情況黎計 隻狗做左舉槍動作"},{"pid":"b890d9059ed7bf70479f815f69f9dff096b230d7","tid":1610271,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf2096836dafb7e519d5907ad4045a41cc3a149","tid":1610271,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12153bea06a0bf7bc6444d8dd6d1f248a7614c85","tid":1610271,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734e854c9f78f57f694f7dae936cc87ae54d0ee5","tid":1610271,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e692591babf7683d7c4abd1e35df1e1185ecdd6d","tid":1610271,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:59:23.000Z","msg":"香港人！！！！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還拖！！！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2d232e6be400592740c8d559dc3892ec99c07b09","tid":1610271,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe3b8c134e7d848e46c8e489c583e38b6860ecc","tid":1610271,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff6bb51d8bec0e7b124cf8d567f7790c227d17c","tid":1610271,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:02:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0868d9fbbe01b32151624f66e0a463bb3e5e11","tid":1610271,"uid":35125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:04:11.000Z","msg":"唯一合理解釋就係狗想殺人"},{"pid":"a16a0fa1eaa0653bec